{"title":"跋涉的梦","authors":["金哲"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金哲［朝鲜族］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知从何时起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦骑在驼峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做梦的老人不知"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠却懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年拐走的遥远的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠远处的驼峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载走老人虚幻的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是他的一簇山羊胡子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衰老得苍白如雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦，不停地跋涉于沙漠中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于累倒了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摔碎了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做梦做得疲惫了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦便碎了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽得像是仇人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海市蜃楼常常不期而至"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生的黄昏里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又多了一次希望和失望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缄默铸造了性格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤独注入足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连变了色的梦的色泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在粗犷的西北风中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻易地失去光色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦在走着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在无际的沙漠留下长长的诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押上悲壮的韵脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用男子汉粗糙的嗓音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向大地和苍穹发出呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代接一代缄默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代接一代跋涉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上盔甲奋力射去箭镞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪杰的威风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷起烽火台上滚滚狼烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠上遗失了廉价的青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今何处寻觅零散的忆念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在驼峰上眺望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲行的路不见尽头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从酣梦中醒来的老人不知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧嚣的森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织出未来绿色的神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金学泉译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}